      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines the creation of a student dashboard web application. It will leverage Wix CMS to manage student records and provide a user interface for viewing and managing this data. Due to the absence of specific Wix Apps for authentication and advanced client-side logic, the plan focuses on data management capabilities provided by Wix CMS."
    },
    {
      "id": "key-features",
      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **View Student Records**: Displays a list of all student records.\n- **View Student Details**: Shows detailed information for a single student record.\n- **Add Student Record**: Allows for the creation of new student records.\n- **Edit Student Record**: Enables modification of existing student records.\n- **Delete Student Record**: Allows for the removal of student records.\n- **Search Student Records**: Provides functionality to search for student records by name or semester.\n- **Manage Attendance and Marks**: Displays and allows management of student attendance and marks within a single view.",
